"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Top Iranian leaders talk about strong unity after Trump's comments about infighting in the country's leadership.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iranian Leaders Discuss Unity\",            \"translated_version\": \"L\u00edderes de Ir\u00e1n hablan sobre unidad fuerte despu\u00e9s de comentarios de Trump sobre peleas en el liderazgo del pa\u00eds.\",            \"translated_title\": \"L\u00edderes de Ir\u00e1n Hablan de Unidad\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Meta is planning its biggest layoff since 2023, which employees have been expecting for weeks.\",            \"english_title\": \"Meta Plans Big Layoff\",            \"translated_version\": \"Meta planea su mayor despido desde 2023, que los empleados han estado esperando por semanas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Meta Planea Gran Despido\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Central Command has stopped 33 ships since starting a blockade on vessels going to and from Iran.\",            \"english_title\": \"Central Command Stops Ships\",            \"translated_version\": \"Comando Central ha detenido 33 barcos desde que comenz\u00f3 un bloqueo a barcos que van y vienen de Ir\u00e1n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Comando Central Detiene Barcos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Gannon Ken Van Dyke is accused of making trades on Polymarket using secret information, according to the justice department.\",            \"english_title\": \"Accusation Against Gannon Ken Van Dyke\",            \"translated_version\": \"Gannon Ken Van Dyke es acusado de hacer intercambios en Polymarket usando informaci\u00f3n secreta, seg\u00fan el departamento de justicia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acusaci\u00f3n Contra Gannon Ken Van Dyke\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ahmed Shihab-Eldin faced charges for spreading false information after sharing images abo